(549, '''Amanah', '\\^hnma\\^ ''Amanah', '\\\\am-aw-naw''\\\\', 'the same as \\\\0548\\\\', '', 'n pr loc', 'Amana 1, variant for Abana 1', 2, ' Amana = "support"\r\n\r\n 1) a river flowing into the plain of Damascus from Antilebanon\r\n 2) mountainous area of the river''s origin\r\n'),
