(740, '''Ari''el', '\\^layra\\^ ''Ari''el', '\\\\ar-ee-ale''\\\\', 'the same as \\\\0739\\\\', '', 'n pr m, f', 'Ariel 6', 6, ' Ariel = "lion of God" or "lioness of God"\r\n\r\n 1) a name applied to Jerusalem\r\n 2) the name of a chief of the returning exiles\r\n'),
