(1297, 'b@ram', '\\^Mrb\\^ b@ram (Aramaic)', '\\\\ber-am''\\\\', 'perhaps from \\\\07313\\\\ with a prepositional prefix', 'TWOT - 2642', 'adv', 'but 2, yet 2, nevertheless 1', 5, ' 1) only, nevertheless, but\r\n'),
