(1299, 'baraq', '\\^qrb\\^ baraq', '\\\\baw-rak''\\\\', 'a primitive root', 'TWOT - 287', 'v', 'cast forth 1', 1, ' 1) (Qal) to flash lightning, cast forth (lightning)\r\n'),
