(2063, 'zo''th', '\\^taz\\^ zo''th', '\\\\zothe''\\\\', 'irregular of \\\\02088\\\\', 'TWOT - 528', 'demons pron f / adv', 'this, her, thus, herein, the same, herewith, that, such', 41, ' 1) this, this one, here, which, this...that, the one...the other, such\r\n    1a) (alone)\r\n        1a1) this one\r\n        1a2) this...that, the one...the other, another\r\n    1b) (appos to subst)\r\n        1b1) this\r\n    1c) (as predicate)\r\n        1c1) this, such\r\n    1d) (enclitically)\r\n        1d1) then\r\n        1d2) who, whom\r\n        1d3) how now, what now\r\n        1d4) what now\r\n        1d5) wherefore now\r\n        1d6) behold here\r\n        1d7) just now\r\n        1d8) now, now already\r\n    1e) (poetry)\r\n        1e1) wherein, which, those who\r\n    1f) (with prefixes)\r\n        1f1) in this (place) here, then\r\n        1f2) on these conditions, herewith, thus provided, by, through\r\n             this, for this cause, in this matter\r\n        1f3) thus and thus\r\n        1f4) as follows, things such as these, accordingly, to that\r\n             effect, in like manner, thus and thus\r\n        1f5) from here, hence, on one side...on the other side\r\n        1f6) on this account\r\n        1f7) in spite of this, which, whence, how\r\n'),
