(3920, 'lakad', '\\^dkl\\^ lakad', '\\\\law-kad''\\\\', 'a primitive root', 'TWOT - 1115', 'v', 'take 112, catch 5, at all 1, frozen 1, holden 1, stick together 1', 121, ' 1) to capture, take, seize\r\n    1a) (Qal)\r\n        1a1) to capture, seize\r\n        1a2) to capture (of men) (fig.)\r\n        1a3) to take (by lot)\r\n    1b) (Niphal)\r\n        1b1) to be captured\r\n        1b2) to be caught (of men in trap, snare) (fig.)\r\n    1c) (Hithpael) to grasp each other\r\n'),
