(5554, 'Cela`', '\\^elo\\^ Cela`', '\\\\seh''-lah\\\\', 'the same as \\\\05553\\\\', '', 'n pr loc', 'Sela 1, Selah 1', 2, ' Sela = "the rock"\r\n\r\n 1) a place in Edom\r\n    1a) perhaps an early name for ''Petra''\r\n'),
