(6286, 'pa''ar', '\\^rap\\^ pa''ar', '\\\\paw-ar''\\\\', 'a primitive root', 'TWOT - 1726,1727', 'v', 'glorify 7, beautify 3, boast 1,go over the boughs 1, Glory 1, vaunt 1', 14, ' 1) to glorify, beautify, adorn\r\n    1a) (Piel) to glorify, beautify\r\n    1b) (Hithpael)\r\n        1b1) to glorify oneself\r\n        1b2) to get glory to oneself, be glorified\r\n 2) (Piel) to go over the boughs\r\n'),
